The Polish act Fading Colours finally returns with new material
and this 10 years after their successful release "I'm Scared
Of..." featuring Anne Clark on the "Eveline" track.
The new album "Come" is released as a double CD in a pretty nice
digipak including the album "I Had To Come" plus a bonus disc
which is entitled "Time Of The Returning".
